$interpreted: Misa: Joshua, what happened to your face...
Misa: N-No, more importantly, why do you have this medicine?
Joshua: ...More important...is that so?
Misa: Um, no...that's not what I meant...
Misa: I...I'm sorry.
Joshua: No, it doesn't matter.
Joshua: For a false Holy Maiden like yourself, getting your power back is more important than my face.
Joshua: If you want more medicine, then come with me.
Misa: Wait...
Misa: ...This landscape...I've seen it before...ah!
Misa: Wait!
Joshua: ...What's the matter?
Misa: This is...! Are you bringing me to——
Misa: ...*cough*...*cough*...!!
Joshua: The underground sewer that the High Priest Devious once used, that's right.
Misa: And you brought me here!?
Misa: Didn't you know that after the High Priest...after Devious died, the Queen had the army seal off the sewer!?
Joshua: Of course I'm aware. Otherwise, bringing you here would be meaningless.
Misa: What...
Lizard Soldier: Who's there!?
Joshua: Oh, speak of the devil. It's the soldiers on patrol.
Lizard Soldier: Name yourself!? This place was sealed off by order of the Queen. Unauthorized personnel are not permitted to enter, leave immed——
Lizard Soldier: ...Eh...?
Joshua: The politicians and the religious once functioned as rivals in this kingdom.
Joshua: If the fallen Holy Maiden were to resist the royal army, as well as sneak into the High Priest's former secret laboratory...
Joshua: ...well, if the Queen were to hear about this, don't how would she view it...
Lizard Soldier: You...little...bastard...
Misa: Stop!
Misa: No, this injury...
Joshua: You're not going to save him? Time's running out, "Holy Maiden".
Misa: Hold on, the blood will stop soon.
Misa: ...*cough*...*cough*...
Lizard Soldier: ...Are you...the Holy Maiden...Misa...?
Lizard Soldier: ...*gasp*...
Misa: Lost consciousness...
Joshua: ...The effects of the medicine last for some time. But once it's taken, the side effects kick in.
Misa: Are you mad!? Hurting people for no reason!? This is not the Joshua I know!
Joshua: ...Is that so? I'm not as certain as you are.
Joshua: The Misa I know, perhaps she's never changed. She's always been a weak, vain, false Holy Maiden.
Misa: What did you say!? You dare sully my reputation——
Misa: ...Dishonor the Snake God and Goddess...
Joshua: What? Cat got your tongue?
Misa: I......
Lizard Captain: ——Holy Maiden Misa!?
Lizard Soldier: Captain! Isn't the lizard soldier on the ground from the Saloo Squad?

Lizard Captain: The Holy Maiden...shouldn't you be confined to the Shrine, thinking of your past errors? Yet you've come down here. 
You weren't thinking of bringing those nasty experiments out of here, were you...?
Misa: No, I would never——
Joshua: Don't you want the medicine?
Joshua: The medicine is in the sewer. Whether you want to go get it...well, that's up to you.
Misa: Oh......
Lizard Captain: You traitors, what are you up to!?
Joshua: Well? If we don't go in now, after today, the queen will be sure to take precautions.
Joshua: Even if you wanted to get it, you wouldn't be able to.
Misa: ...Shut up! Shut up! I know all this, you don't have to tell me!
